data.description: Mother, mother ocean! Wake up to the sound of waves crashing and bask in panoramic nature views from the multiple decks of this home. This coastal home seamlessly integrates indoor and outdoor living spaces, creating an open, airy atmosphere that captures the essence of coastal living. A short walk from your steps onto sandy shores, ensures every day is a beach day. The owners suite and 2 bedrooms are on the first floor, with a loft and additional bathroom in the loft that offers the feeling of privacy in both areas of the home. This coast home offers unparalleled natural beauty. Whether you’re seeking a year-round residence or a vacation escape, this property invites you to experience the ultimate in coastal living. Seize this opportunity to own a piece of paradise. Arrange your private tour today.
